strings.Value: "I grow tired of dirty tents and thick-skulled barbarians. The First World was by far more interesting..."
"Every place is better than a stinking barbarian camp. Well... almost any place."
"But those barbarians do know how to have fun, hehe! — At least the ones who haven't thrown in with the damn cultists."
"At least barbarians stink less than Fistword – or your cities!"
"Yes, it's a magical place! But I'm afraid we'll grow bored of its vistas, and in the end miss our simple lands, where people don't keep changing their appearance!"
